eatedDate_Day')\")}};\r\n\r\nAppFee_curr = filter TotalFees_curr by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' in [\"Business License Application\", \"Individual Application\"];\r\nAppFee_prev = filter TotalFees_prev by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' in [\"Business License Application\", \"Individual Application\"];\r\n\r\nLicenseFee_curr = filter TotalFees_curr by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Business License\";\r\nLicenseFee_prev = filter TotalFees_prev by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Business License\";\r\n\r\nRegCodViolFee_curr = filter TotalFees_curr by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Regulatory Code Violation\";\r\nRegCodViolFee_prev = filter TotalFees_prev by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Regulatory Code Violation\";\r\n\r\nRegEnfActFee_curr = filter TotalFees_curr by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Violation Enforcement Action\";\r\nRegEnfActFee_prev = filter TotalFees_prev by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Violation Enforcement Action\";\r\n\r\nInspecFee_curr = filter TotalFees_curr by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Inspection\";\r\nInspecFee_prev = filter TotalFees_prev by 'RegulatoryTransactionFeeSource' == \"Inspection\";\r\n\r\nresult = group TotalFees_curr by all full, AppFee_curr by all full, TotalFees_prev by all full, AppFee_prev by all full, LicenseFee_curr by all full, LicenseFee_prev by all full, RegCodViolFee_curr by all full, RegCodViolFee_prev by all full, RegEnfActFee_curr by all full, RegEnfActFee_prev by all full, InspecFee_curr by all full, InspecFee_prev by all;\r\n\r\nresult = foreach result generate sum(TotalFees_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'TotalFees', sum(AppFee_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'ApplicationsFee', sum(LicenseFee_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'IssuedLicensesFees', sum(RegCodViolFee_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'ViolationsFees', sum(RegEnfActFee_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'EnforcementActionsFees', sum(InspecFee_curr.'TotalFeeAmount') as 'InspectionsFee',sum(TotalFees_prev.'TotalFeeAmount') as '